01:43:40.262 --> 01:43:52.149
Please take my life and forgive him! Forgive? How can I forgive anyone, when I can't even recognize my mother's belongings?

398
01:43:53.859 --> 01:44:04.870
Remember this? A symbol of our relationship. Without this, I'd still be a plaything for her enemies.

399
01:44:05.370 --> 01:44:15.756
So let me ask, why'd you bring me this? I was sincerely looking after your well-being... My well-being?

400
01:44:17.424 --> 01:44:29.269
I used it to solidify my throne, and you regained power. Your sincerity is noted. So can I throw it away now?

401
01:44:33.607 --> 01:44:48.288
Your Highness! But it's your mother's article! It's my mother's, so why do you care? The late king worried about seeds of trouble,

402
01:44:49.831 --> 01:45:02.261
so any articles that belonged to the queen were all destroyed. Father...

403
01:45:09.476 --> 01:45:12.306
Did you really took me for a fool?

404
01:45:12.479 --> 01:45:26.577
The late queen was indeed killed by conspiracy... I'll ask again! When a king makes an error, should his subjects object,

405
01:45:26.577 --> 01:45:40.215
or should they comply for the fear of their lives? A loyal subject should... Pandering to my needs, regardless of its consequences, you're a treacherous subject!

406
01:45:43.051 --> 01:45:57.566
you're a traitor who ruined this nation! Your Highness! Please take my life! No loyal servants exist in my court,

407
01:46:00.861 --> 01:46:07.868
But a dog should not be put down over one bite.

408
01:46:24.843 --> 01:46:32.476
A father, who offered his own wife's keepsake, and his son, who offered his lover.

409
01:46:37.898 --> 01:46:41.860
What will you do for me now?

410
01:46:45.572 --> 01:46:48.617
Can you bring me paint for the drawing?

411
01:47:51.096 --> 01:48:04.943
This is my reward to you, so retain your loyalty. I'm eternally grateful. And recruit for the next group of comforters. No mistakes this time.

412
01:48:04.943 --> 01:48:06.570
Yes, Your Majesty.

413
01:48:43.982 --> 01:48:47.569
That is the reason why I kept you alive.

414
01:48:55.702 --> 01:48:57.120
This was your sister's,

415
01:49:00.541 --> 01:49:11.927
I'd have used it too, to avenge a sister who met a shameful death. Shouldn't have trusted a whore.

416
01:49:14.096 --> 01:49:28.944
Care for an amusement? When blood river soaks the dry land, old boat's clamors shake the world! Cowardly boatman! Seize the moment to build a new boat!

417
01:49:31.864 --> 01:49:35.909
Treacherous words from a treacherous subject.

418
01:49:38.829 --> 01:49:52.885
Round everyone up! Close the door, another purge is coming! Hide yourself, they'll take you away! You are all pigs!

419
01:49:58.557 --> 01:50:13.488
That is the very reason of your life! Peasant blood and sweat fueled the king's madness, it knew no boundary.

420
01:50:13.488 --> 01:50:25.375
If the screams of his populace don't stop his dance, he must be stopped at any cost. When IM returns with new comforters,

421
01:50:25.375 --> 01:50:39.598
public's rage will be at its limit, we'll start the rebellion. You bastards! Heaven will judge you. Go to hell, you bastards! Don't you have family?!

422
01:51:00.869 --> 01:51:03.330
Why is everyone so desperate to die?

423
01:51:25.894 --> 01:51:31.525
Where is everyone? Due to long travel, I've allowed them to rest.

424
01:51:31.525 --> 01:51:38.031
But I should at least greet them! They will look better when they are rested.

425
01:51:40.492 --> 01:51:55.215
All right, I can wait a night. You must also be tired, so rest up. Go now. Take a rest.

426
01:52:05.100 --> 01:52:09.563
Anyone there? Yes, Your Highness, are you all right?

427
01:52:11.648 --> 01:52:26.622
Pardon me? I wish to see the comforters now. But I must alert the security guards... You can be my security detail! Get ready at once! Your Highness, Minister IM is here.

428
01:52:29.541 --> 01:52:43.013
Soong-jae! If you had everything ready, you should've told me before I got drunk. Forgive me. I was too conscious of others. It's okay, very good.

429
01:52:44.014 --> 01:52:56.235
Everyone's so afraid of me, always, 'Your Highness!' Shut the hell up! Damn it! - Soong-jae! - Yes, bud!

430
01:52:56.777 --> 01:53:02.991
Let's have some real fun, like we did as kids!

431
01:53:21.969 --> 01:53:31.603
What's going on? Don't joke around! Do you remember? The girl role play, that you liked? What?

432
01:53:32.271 --> 01:53:45.993
Now, you take the role that I always had to play. You must be mad! If you want it intact, hide it.

433
01:53:54.042 --> 01:53:56.044
What's going on?!

434
01:54:01.800 --> 01:54:11.101
Don't be upset over the past. I understand, I'll forget about this. So sheath your sword.

435
01:54:14.813 --> 01:54:28.035
Sheath your sword! The world will be better off without it. Fine, fine. You think I won't do it? I will...

436
01:54:48.472 --> 01:54:49.473
Yes, Lord!

437
01:55:08.992 --> 01:55:18.001
Contempt for the king won't go unpunished! I only see a murderer, so where is the king?

438
01:55:38.105 --> 01:55:50.033
Why are you doing this? Evil wins power, so all desire to be more evil. It's the source of our tragedy, and what tortures your soul! I shall uproot it.

439
01:55:50.576 --> 01:56:03.297
Even if I die, you can't take my place! Friend! Evil is replaced by a greater evil. You underestimate me!

440
01:56:09.011 --> 01:56:15.017
Your Highness. I'll bring out the comforters, and leave you be.

441
01:56:15.601 --> 01:56:28.197
Pale skin, full buttocks, sharp nose tip. They fit your taste, so please fulfill your duty as a king. You bastard!

442
01:56:29.489 --> 01:56:32.034
Stop right there!

443
01:57:10.781 --> 01:57:11.990
Let's go!

444
01:57:15.619 --> 01:57:25.420
Do not back down! We must take the palace! Captain!

445
01:57:28.090 --> 01:57:36.181
Minister YU, you brought reinforcement. We can't last very long this way. Still no orders from the king? He's nowhere to be found.

446
01:57:40.185 --> 01:57:44.356
The palace gate is open! Advance!

447
01:57:46.233 --> 01:57:57.244
Minister! What took you so long? I want nothing more than to save this country!

448
01:57:58.203 --> 01:58:05.252
I heard that fox Soong-jae visited you. How can you lead the uprising with his help?

449
01:58:11.842 --> 01:58:15.220
And, I know I'm late to the party,

450
01:58:15.220 --> 01:58:21.185
but reserve me a spot in the court. Advance!

451
01:58:26.273 --> 01:58:31.236
IM Soong-jae!

452
01:58:33.947 --> 01:58:47.336
Are you not afraid of the heavens?! Do you not know who I am?! Of course we do! A former concubine, who feeds off the populace, you're just a temptress who fueled tyranny!

453
01:58:49.171 --> 01:58:57.429
You're just a pathetic pawn! I was a loyal subject... Die, you bitch!

454
01:59:26.500 --> 01:59:32.589
you call this shame? It wouldn't be enough to rip you to shreds!

455
01:59:38.512 --> 01:59:41.849
What are you waiting for? Kill me!

456
01:59:58.448 --> 02:00:09.251
how am I any different from the mad king? If you could at least laugh at me... Stay alive.

457
02:00:10.586 --> 02:00:19.928
Your sins will not wash away so easily. Survive and live to undo all your wrongs. Undo everything.

458
02:00:22.723 --> 02:00:30.230
Majesty, I'll take care of her, please stay back! Your Highness!

459
02:00:33.233 --> 02:00:37.863
Why're you wearing the king's robe?

460
02:00:40.657 --> 02:00:54.046
What have you done to deserve it?! A hero is a nobody during peace, and a moral man is useless on the battlefield. What's the difference? Father!

461
02:00:57.508 --> 02:01:09.770
Where did you hide the king? We should kill him first! Power cannot be contained. Nonsense! Like you said, we can build a higher levee! Have you gone blind? You're the blind one!

462
02:01:09.770 --> 02:01:20.822
I know you started everything for that bitch! Move aside, I'll kill her and bring you back! Enough!

463
02:01:21.782 --> 02:01:26.745
This is the only way for me as your son.

464
02:01:32.751 --> 02:01:36.046
No, no, please! Please no! Please!

465
02:01:37.798 --> 02:01:50.185
No! No! Soong-jae, my son! For upholding tyranny, creating a mad king,

466
02:01:50.602 --> 02:02:05.117
blinding you with power, being a terrible son, I'll pay for it all. Please... No, you have to live!

467
02:02:05.117 --> 02:02:13.625
How can I face your mother if you die like this? - No, please! - Fools... How did you not know?

468
02:02:19.673 --> 02:02:26.263
You destroyed both of us. We could have accomplished so much together.

469
02:03:00.005 --> 02:03:13.977
Drinking bud, it will only end by taking my life, right? Do you have a last wish? Take that whore, and send her far away.

470
02:03:14.978 --> 02:03:17.022
She's rather irritating.

471
02:03:34.998 --> 02:03:45.050
I had the king and the world at my fingertips. I had my share of the world.

472
02:03:45.634 --> 02:03:51.974
Your vile reputation will last a millennium.

473
02:03:57.729 --> 02:04:00.983
The king is not here, move out!

474
02:04:09.032 --> 02:04:15.289
Rest easy now.

475
02:04:56.955 --> 02:05:01.335
Go on and take them.

476
02:05:06.006 --> 02:05:11.428
The pigs had the last laugh!

477
02:05:15.974 --> 02:05:23.482
After Joseon's first uprising, The Beauty Recruits perished With King Yeonsan-gun.

478
02:05:37.037 --> 02:05:48.006
Not quite selection process, but exercising power that was given. How could I best explain this?

479
02:05:49.758 --> 02:06:02.771
So what happened to the mad king in the end? Haven't you been listening? His sexual appetite got him banished, so comforters were what got him killed! Good riddance!

480
02:06:07.776 --> 02:06:22.749
Yeah! The IMs tried to help a concubine, and the two were found in ashes. Do that to me too!

481
02:06:25.794 --> 02:06:36.763
and they deserved the worst fate in the world. If your drinks are empty, get going! Hurry!

482
02:06:40.100 --> 02:06:41.810
It's here! It's starting!

483
02:06:59.286 --> 02:07:13.800
the two IMs were up to no good, so desperate to get on the king's good side, can't just let this cruelty continue!

484
02:07:13.800 --> 02:07:28.732
The enraged mountain god sent a tiger! I'm gonna hurt my back! Empty your pockets!

485
02:07:33.445 --> 02:07:39.243
It searched the world for deluded subjects,

486
02:07:39.243 --> 02:07:48.794
It searched and searched but could not find them. Hidden behind a human mask, can't tell what's in his heart.

487
02:07:51.505 --> 02:08:01.181
All right, feed on my body, and if you're a good man, I'll strengthen your body,

488
02:08:01.181 --> 02:08:06.770
or I'll become poison and kill you.

489
02:08:14.736 --> 02:08:16.989
I found you!

